%package -n libdb_cxx4.7
Summary: C++ API to Berkeley DB
Group: System Environment/Libraries
Obsoletes: db-cxx < %{version}-%{release}
Conflicts: db-cxx < %{version}-%{release}

%description -n libdb_cxx4.7
